The '''Artichoke''' is a [[Vegetables|vegetable]] [[Crops|crop]] that grows from [[Artichoke Seeds]] after 8 days.  The seeds are available from [[Pierre's General Store]] starting in Year 2.

Artichoke can be acquired before Year 2 through the use of [[Mixed Seeds]].  Artichokes can then be placed in a [[Seed Maker]] to produce [[Artichoke Seeds]].

